<br>
Why would you want a mod to all insturment types?  At this stage in the game where bards have struggled so hard to get insturment mods on a variety of items, why would you want to set us back 3 years and make all high end items with focuses less than whatever said mod on Epic2.0 will be, completly useless?  And in turn this would bind us to the epic as we were bound to Epic1.0.  Not to mention that an All-Insturment mod around 3.0 would make all insturments nearly useless as well with the current insturment mod cap; why would you switch out your weapon for insturments to gain such marginal increase in song effectiveness for a relativly large loss in melee dps output?<br>
