I believe that the suggested &quot;Stack mod&quot; to all, or a single (voice) mod is a viable option, since it would make both the Epic2.0 and current insturment mod items desireable, although a &quot;stack mod&quot; of 1.0 is fairly unreasonable, since it would make items such as qvic armor nearly as potent as our best current insturments, and equally as potent when cap is considered.  Another option might be to give the Epic2.0 a worn effect that raises the insturment mod cap a significant amount (such as 50), or removes it completly.<br>
